f_{X,Y}
 f_{X,Y}(x,y) = cxe^{-x}1_{x>0}1_{\left|y\right|<x}. 
\left\{x\in\mathbb{R}:\ 1_{x>0}1_{\left|y\right|<x}\right\} = \left\{x\in\mathbb{R}:1_{x>\text{max}(0,\left|y\right|)}\right\}
f_{X|Y}(x|y)
f_{Y|X}(y|x)
\int_{x\in \Omega_X}f_{X|Y}(x|y)\mathrm{d}x=1
\int_{y\in \Omega_Y}f_{Y|X}(y|x)\mathrm{d}y=1
